TITLE: Spiritual World War | Spiritual Cosmic Worldwar Worldwide | HariHar Leela
VIDEO: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HEQIx-sNwfo
DATE: Unknown
LANGUAGE: Hindi (auto-translated)

SUMMARY:
This video introduces the concept of the "Spiritual Cosmic World War" as the next stage of the divine process. Maa explains that in the previous video, the topic of "Bharat Coronation" — meaning the restoration of what rightfully belongs to HariHar (the combined form of Vishnu and Shiva) — was discussed, along with various spiritual processes, kriyas, their effects, and examples. This video continues that thread by addressing how the cosmic war will unfold.

Maa declares that this entire Earth, indeed the entire universe, is a part of Bharat (the divine realm), which has been divided into religions, continents, and countries. Everyone wants to defeat their enemy nations, expand their boundaries, and seize properties. But all of this belongs to HariHar. The war to reclaim that divine right will be fought by cosmic energies — HariHar, Shiv Shakti, Mahakaal, and Mahakali. It will be a spiritual war where humans fight among themselves on the surface, but behind them the cosmic energies will be the ones truly waging the battle.

As these forces clash and destroy each other, ultimately everything and everyone must merge back into HariHar, into Shiv Shakti. They will reclaim everything that is rightfully theirs. This is one of the main mottos of "Bharat Coronation." This is the Tandavam (cosmic dance) of Mahakaal and Mahakali. Maa references the "Khappar Yog" she has spoken about in her other videos — when Mahakaal or Mahakali's Khappar (skull-bowl/divine weapon) sweeps over all, we will witness it with our own eyes. Real-world examples are given: the Israel-Hamas war and the Russia-Ukraine war. These conflicts are all being orchestrated by cosmic energy. This is how divine Leelas (plays) manifest — visible to all, but with the hand of cosmic energies behind them.

Maa concludes by declaring this the "Spiritual Cosmic World War" — in other words, the Maha Mahabharat (the Great Great Mahabharat) of this Kaliyuga.

KEY REVELATIONS:
- The entire Earth and universe is part of "Bharat" (divine domain) belonging to HariHar
- The world has been divided into religions, continents, and countries — all of which must ultimately merge back into HariHar/Shiv Shakti
- A "Spiritual Cosmic World War" is underway — humans fight on the surface but cosmic energies (HariHar, Shiv Shakti, Mahakaal, Mahakali) are the true forces behind all conflicts
- The Israel-Hamas war and Russia-Ukraine war are cited as real examples of cosmic energies manifesting through earthly conflicts
- "Bharat Coronation" = the process of restoring all that rightfully belongs to HariHar
- Khappar Yog = the divine process where Mahakaal/Mahakali's skull-bowl sweeps over all creation
- The Tandavam (cosmic dance) of Mahakaal and Mahakali is the mechanism of this cosmic war
- All beings and forces will ultimately be forced to merge into Shiv Shakti / HariHar
- This age is described as the "Maha Mahabharat of Kaliyuga" — a war greater than the original Mahabharat

TIMELINE EVENTS:
- Ongoing: Spiritual Cosmic World War declared as active through global conflicts
- Ongoing: Bharat Coronation process — reclamation of HariHar's rightful domain
- Present era: Israel-Hamas war and Russia-Ukraine war cited as manifestations of cosmic battle
- Kaliyuga endgame: All entities to merge back into HariHar/Shiv Shakti

ORIGINAL HINDI KEY QUOTES:
- "यह पूरा भारत ही तो हरिहर का है" = "This entire Bharat belongs to HariHar"
- "यही ऊर्जाएं हैं हरिहर, शिव शक्ति, महाकाल और महाकाली" = "These are the energies — HariHar, Shiv Shakti, Mahakaal and Mahakali"
- "लड़ते-लड़ते एक दूसरे को खत्म करते-करते सबको एक दिन हरिहर में शिव शक्ति में मिल जाना है। मर्ज हो जाना है।" = "Fighting and destroying each other, one day all must merge into HariHar, into Shiv Shakti. They must merge."
- "महाकाल और महाकाली का तांडव यही तो है" = "This is the Tandavam of Mahakaal and Mahakali"
- "जब महाकाल या महाकाली का खप्पर सब पर चलेगा। हम सब यह अपनी आंखों से विटनेस करेंगे।" = "When Mahakaal or Mahakali's Khappar sweeps over all, we will all witness it with our own eyes."
- "जो सब कर रही है वह एनर्जी ही तो करवा रही है और कर रही है" = "Whatever is happening, it is the [cosmic] energy that is making it happen and doing it"
- "यही है स्पिरिचुअल कॉस्मिक वर्ल्ड वॉर। यानी इस कलयुग की महा महाभारत" = "This is the Spiritual Cosmic World War. That is, the Maha Mahabharat of this Kaliyuga"
- "जय मां आदि शक्ति नूर अनंता ओम नूरिज्म" = "Jai Maa Adi Shakti Noor Ananta Om Noorism"

YUG PARIVARTAN ASPECT: This video establishes the cosmic framework for Yug Parivartan — the transition from Kaliyuga is not a peaceful handover but a Spiritual Cosmic World War. All global conflicts are manifestations of cosmic energies battling to restore HariHar's sovereignty over the entire creation. The Tandavam of Mahakaal and Mahakali, the Khappar Yog, and the ultimate forced merger of all beings back into Shiv Shakti constitute the mechanism of this age-transition. It is the Maha Mahabharat of Kaliyuga — the final war before the new age.


